062c\u064e\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650\u0639\u064e \u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u062f\u064f\u0651\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34708,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/21\/dua-good-qadr\/","url_meta":{"origin":21935,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Qadr: I ask for Your every decree to be good","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 21, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, taught her among the comprehensive supplications, \u201cO Allah, I ask You for Your every decree upon me to be good.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 3846 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20676,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/06\/08\/dua-refuge-from-my-evil\/","url_meta":{"origin":21935,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: I seek refuge in You from evil I have done","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would say in his supplications, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in you from the evil I have done and the evil I have not done.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2716 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9621,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/01\/salat-ala-nabi\/","url_meta":{"origin":21935,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salawat: Dedicating supplications to bless the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 1, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ubayy ibn Ka\u2019b reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I send blessings upon you often. How many of my prayers should be for blessings upon you?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cAs you wish.\u201d I said, \u201cA fourth?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cAs you wish, but more is better for you.\u201d I\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25289,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/22\/increase-dua-prophet-jumuah\/","url_meta":{"origin":21935,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jumu&#8217;ah: Supplications for the Prophet on Friday","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIncrease your supplications for me on the day and night of Friday. Whoever blesses me once, Allah will bless him ten times.\u201d Source: al-Sunan al-Kubra\u0301 lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 5994 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34009,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/02\/16\/dua-for-a-windy-storm\/","url_meta":{"origin":21935,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Rain: The Prophet\u2019s supplication for a windy storm","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 16, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, if there was a windy storm, he would say, \u201cO Allah, I ask You for its good, the good within it, and the good for which it was sent. I seek refuge in You from its evil, the evil within\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/21935","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https: